## LED test / Diagnostic mode / Network connection: 

* Oranage solid: It does have an IP and pass DHCP (It can be blocked) 
* Orange flashing : Router and DHCP no IPs 
* Green Solid: Ethernet cable is working
* Green blinking: Ethernet cable down
* Solid red: End/ Begin of the cycle

### LED Lights/ Status lights

* Solid White - Sonos is working
* Solid blue - Bluetooth
* Flashing blue - Pairing mode
* Solid red - Amp foult, time out after factory reset, update error 
* Solid green
* Solid amber
Refer to: https://support.sonos.com/en-us/article/sonos-led-lights
